{"tid":2307277,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"北約報告稱要認真思考如何應對中國的崛起","createTime":"2020-12-01T05:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:42:27.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ce320544775bbd2b86773246e2722c365f97b95","tid":2307277,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"北約報告稱要認真思考如何應對中國的崛起<br />\n<br />\n北約將於星期二發表報告，表示要更認真思考，如何應對中國的崛起。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，北約應該保持對中國的技術優勢，保護電腦網絡和基建，並與澳洲等非北約國家，建立更緊密關係，以及關注中國正在建立的太空威懾。<br />\n<br />\n北約秘書長斯托爾滕貝格表示，中國的崛起對北約的安全構成重要挑戰，舉例中國正大規模投資新武器，從北極到非洲，都正在趕上，中國的價值觀與他們不同，並嘗試恫嚇其他國家。<br />\n<br />\n有北約外交官說，中國不再是西方期望的良性貿易夥伴，而是本世紀的崛起力量，北約必須適應，但不會宣布中國是對手。"},{"pid":"1b471af2a47a6296e0df0e6fe7157d3174ce6ff0","tid":2307277,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562885-20201201.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562885-20201201.htm&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0pmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=09e4dd41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562885-20201201.htm&h=c3b1859d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562885-20201201.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9ee8eec6f8d61992514ed465028acd67ae86ac54","tid":2307277,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"某国四方樹敵，八面威風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a731584655aa951aa490f1ef69df361fd567b59f","tid":2307277,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:40:53.000Z","msg":"//中國的崛起對北約的安全構成重要挑戰，舉例中國正大規模投資新武器，從北極到非洲，都正在趕上，